						               													<description>Unofficial fan-made board game based on the Castlevania series, previously available to download as a free print and play until Konami demanded in November 2018 that it be taken down.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is mostly co-op, and loosely based on Castlevania 2: Simon's Quest. 2-6 players work together to fight their way through the castle while a curse is slowly killing all of them. The goal is to move through the castle, fighting monsters and overcoming various traps and other events, to gather 5 parts of Dracula's body. Bring them to the tower to resurrect Dracula and break the curse before time runs out, and then, hopefully, kill him again to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;13 playable characters to choose from, each with their own deck of unique weapons and skills which are gradually unlocked throughout the game, and plenty of monsters, events, and items, so that no two games are exactly the same.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
